flow.mentorSays:
We can optimize space from O(n) to O(1).

Notice: we only need the previous 2 values!

Instead of:
let rob = [2, 7, 11, 11, 12]

We can use:
let prev2 = 0;  // rob[i-2]
let prev1 = 0;  // rob[i-1]

for (let i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
  let current = Math.max(prev1, nums[i] + prev2);
  prev2 = prev1;
  prev1 = current;
}

Space: O(n) â†’ O(1)
Time: still O(n)

